		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://www.qmtpro.com/~nes/palettes.zip" class="postlink">http://www.qmtpro.com/~nes/palettes.zip</a>, "pc10.pal"
<br />
<br />Regarding the builtin RGB palette in Nintendulator, I deliberately added the extra column of grays because there were several games which looked really bad without them. Perhaps I will add an option to toggle the extra grays in a future version.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
