<br />
<br />There was a special setting I had to enable to allow uploading of non-"preferred" file types. MediaWiki treats them all as "images" normally, but by using a [[Media:filename]] link instead of [[Image:filename]], clicking the link will go directly to the file (rather than placing a broken image tag with a link to an intermediate 'Image summary' page).

		

